            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T06:56:05.94+09:00">The Master said:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:00:14.571+09:00">Shall I teach you the meaning of knowledge?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:09:29.577+09:00">When you know a thing to recognise that you know it,  [Zottoli: quod scis, reputes id scire.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:01:46.598+09:00">and when you do not know that you do not know</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-19a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T07:01:39.843+09:00">-that is knowledge.</seg>
                </p>
